_______________________________________________________________________________
"Psychic Lash"     
        A psionicist can use this ability to blast an opponent
        with raw telepathic power, directly assaulting its mind.
        Though very fast and easy, this attack is unskilled,
        relying purely on its raw force, and therefore has less
        effect than a Psionic Blast or Mental Blow.  The exact
        effect varies slightly with each use, but is not dependent
        on guild level, regular level, or any outside factor.
 
SP Cost:  15            Guild Level:  1         Potential Points:  1
 
Command:  plash <target>
